<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wolfram von Egloffstein</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe der beschlagnahmten Schafe des Erhard Per, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_186" id="92r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_186_r1l1">VVolframen vom Eglofſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_186_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> wolfram Als vvir euch nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r1l3">Erhart Peren <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers vnd ~ ſeiner Schaf wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r1l4">die Jr Jm genomen habt / Alſo hat <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> derſelb ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r1l5">vnſer burger vor vns cʒu den heyligen behabt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r1l6">daʒ <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Schafe ſein reht redlich gekauffts gut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r1l7">ſeẏn vnd die <expan>nymand<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒefluht ſal cʒeſchirm noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r1l8"><expan>cʒugeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> gekaufft hab . hyrümb <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr Jm noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r1l9"><expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ ſeine Schaf gencʒlich <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd on </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r1l10">hindernüſʒ volgen laſſen wöllet durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r1l11">Als etc Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Galli </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_186" id="92r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wolframen vom Eglofstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Wolfram, als wir euch nehst
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Erhart Peren
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers und seiner schaf wegen, die ir im
                        genomen habt, also hat <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> derselb unser
                        burger vor uns czu den heyligen behabt, daz
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> schafe sein reht redlich gekauffts gut
                        seyn und die <expan>nymand<ex>en</ex></expan> cze fluhtsal, cze schirm noch
                            <expan>czu gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> gekaufft hab. Hyrümb
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir im noch
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine schaf genczlich
                                <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und on hindernüsz volgen lassen
                        wöllet durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Galli.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
